		<TextDefinition Key="Subversion.Wc17NoTortoise">
			<Context>detected that a project folder is from a v1.7, but the loaded client lib is v1.6, Tortoise is not present on the machine. This text should normally not be shown because when no forceSVN or Tortoise is present the 1.7 lib gets preselected.</Context>
